          "process_md": "\n1. Applicant students have to visit the [official website.](https://sjmsnew.rajasthan.gov.in/scholarship/)1. Now Select the Login option or Register Option. \n1. Applicants will be redirected to the  Rajasthan [SSO portal](https://sso.rajasthan.gov.in/signin). 1. Now students can log in with their Jan-Aadhaar ID. \n1. Fill out the application form.\n1. Attach the required documents.\n1. Submit.\n\n"
